Freelancing krein gaye bohat saara pesa aayega ,lekin that,s very basic point.

Long-Term Advantages:
* Economy: Agar ap isse sahi tareeke se krtein hai toh isse poore mulk ke liye bohat faida pohanchain ga.
* The Goal Of Freelancing is kay apko financical freedom ki taraf lejati hai.Financial freedom means in short is kay apko peson ka msla nahi hai.It means ap financially free hai.
* Freelancing apko paasive income tak ljati hai.Passive income mtlab ap soye huay hai tab bhi pese aarahay hai.

Short-Term Advantages:
* Flexible Hours: Apne jis time kaam krna hai us time krein.
* Freely to Everywhere: Ap kahin bhi ho kaam krskte hain.
* Earn your own Profit: Ap apna proit apne pas rkh rhay ho apko profit share krne ki zrurat nahi padh rahi hai.
* No Upper Limit: Freelancing mein koi upper limit nahi kamane ke point of view se like ordinary job mein upper limit huti hai kay starting mein employer ki salary 10k hai toh 10 saalon mein woh some lacs hogi ,1 Million,2 million nahi ,freelancing mein yeh scene nahi hai.
* Helath and Family Time Supports: Ap easily dono cheezan focus krskte hai due to no restriction of time during work.